<h1>Watercress</h1>
<hr>

Watercress is a tool to generate a styleguide based on comments within a CSS file. Inspired by KSS, but designed with further automation in mind. Written in Scala with a hint of Java.

Watercress is currently in development. Examples will be forthcoming, pending a stable release.

<h2>Documentation</h2>

To view the latest Scala docs, check out the <a href="http://randak.github.io/watercress/latest/api/#com.kristianrandall.watercress.package">API Documentation</a>

